Directions
From the Florida Turnpike
Exit onto NW 41st Street (Exit #29). Travel east for 1.5 miles. At 102nd Avenue, turn right to the security gatehouse.
From the Palmetto Expressway
Exit onto NW 36th Street. Travel west 2.3 miles and NW 36 Street will curve to become NW 41 Street. At 102nd Avenue turn left to the gatehouse.
Please note that the only entrance to the golf club for the public is through the gate at NW 41st Street and 102nd Avenue. Some directions will lead you to an entrance on 33rd Street. However, this entrance is for residents with transponders only.

Memberships
Membership Options
Costa del Sol Golf Club Members participating in the Program enjoy unlimited playing privileges at Costa del Sol Golf Club subject to applicable cart fees and on a space available basis. Non-Members accompanying Members will pay regular rates.
Additional features:
Members receive a 10% discount on
Golf Lesson
rates.
Cannot be combined with any other discount.
Members will be entitled to discounted rates at special events at Costa del Sol Golf Club.
Please Contact The Pro Shop
305-592-3300
to schedule an appointment and register.

Membership
Privileges
A membership at Costa del Sol Golf Club in Miami, FL, offers golfers unlimited access to a challenging course with beautiful par-5s and par-3s, along with priority booking, practice facilities, and a sense of community. As a community-owned facility, we provide personalized service.
